summary: An Ordinance approving the assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 1718, for the improvement of Eastlake Avenue, in the City of Seattle, between East Roy Street and the south end of the bridge across Lake Union in the extension of Sixth Avenue Northeast, under Ordinance No. 18239 and assessing the amounts thereof against each parcel and lot of land and part thereof shown in said roll, and providing for the collection thereof.
